{"tid":2511503,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"咪再煲大南非/印度變種病毒","createTime":"2021-05-01T03:23:27.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-01T03:41:54.000Z","uid":258706,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"bf6142e22a489c289b8f2fd17106aba9a6c7e33d","tid":2511503,"uid":258706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T03:23:27.000Z","msg":"係咪又想政府揾輿論做藉口收緊防疫措拖？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係咪想變返二人堂食？冇波打？冇街行？<br />\n<br />\n唔想嘅話就靜啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 全港有750萬人口，呢幾日先得唔夠10人中變種病毒，百分比係勁低<br />\n<br />\n過份吹大只會好似先前第二波咁，明明得些少確診 (本地確診唔過50宗) 俾政府用限聚令影響正常生活 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 再加大監控 (eg 所有場合局你用健康碼)<br />\n<br />\n你話政府啲政策愈癲，啲人肯反抗就話有用姐<br />\n但依家睇唔到有人因為防疫措施On 9/限制人權而出嚟抗爭囉<br />\n煲大呢單嘢好處少過壞處<br />\n更多本身有嘅自由繼續被剝削<br />\n<br />\n靜啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 煲大呢單嘢冇好處<br />\n要煲大嘅話，等變種變毒喺香港確診上千單先啦<br />\n咪再做恐懼撚嘞，好冇？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n次次收緊"},{"pid":"73b68af895063ca980ad5090acbb6de52c3f4377","tid":2511503,"uid":327462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T03:24:22.000Z","msg":"無懼撚 拉<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97ed7f6510e4368edf5f11575bf2a25509fb7df3","tid":2511503,"uid":258706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T03:29:59.000Z","msg":"一個二個唔識靜 <img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab6567a0c60980b9023f9a59b3f0b939503ed16b","tid":2511503,"uid":49784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T03:41:54.000Z","msg":"巴打，唔係想話你<br />\n<br />\n但你埋怨連登？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n連登反對係咪就唔會收緊?<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}